This paper is primarily focused on object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses generative modeling and optimization techniques, which are common topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions pedestrian detection, which falls under the subfield of graphics (cs.GR) and medical image analysis, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM).
